                                    <note>7 letters. </note>
                                </msItem>
                                <note>The majority of the letters are edited in <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/102184">DS 1</title>
                                    </bibl> and a sellection in a modern edition in <bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107593">Gejrot (1994)</title>
                                    </bibl>, which also presents a survey of the copy-book and editions of the different letters (see<bibl>
                                        <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107593">Gejrot (1994)</title>
                                        <citedRange from="183" to="196" unit="page"/>
                                    </bibl>). </note>
                            </msItem>
