                                    <foliation>
                                        <locus from="2" to="55" scheme="folios"/>: contemporary pagination in the top margin, 1-190.Items numbered with letters and Roman numerals in the outer margin in red ink. Each parish is assigned a letter (a-i), and each letter a Roman numeral. </foliation>
                                    <condition>Parchment worn and stained. More than half of all original leaves missing. The older pagination indicates 95 leaves, currently 55 full leaves and stubs. See Collation for more information. <locus from="1" to="1" scheme="folios"/>: a 60mm long slash through the middle of the page.</condition>
